1.title: Chapter 1: The Boyz Win the Contest
1.plot: Trystan and Teddy Jenkins win a local radio sweepstakes that awards them an all expenses paid trip to New York City.

2.title: Chapter 2: The Boyz Meet Their Fate
2.plot: The Boyz start their first day in the city and Teddy has a rough start, facing the grim reality of a deadly horoscope.

3.title: Chapter 3: The Boyz Search for their Squad
3.plot: The Boyz decide to try out the Meetup app to find a group of friends in the city.

4.title: Chapter 4: The Boyz Hit their Stride
4.plot: The Boyz split up for the day so Trystan can go to an audition, while Teddy gets an unexpected opportunity.

5.title: Chapter 5: The Boyz Say Goodbye to NYC
5.plot: The boys wrap up their last day in the city and Trystan gets a pep talk from an unlikely stranger.

imdb.plot outline: City Boyz is a five episode original comedy series that follows two adults brothers (Trystan and Teddy Jenkins) who still live at home with their mother, Tamela, in a small town in Florida. The boys win a radio sweepstakes with a video submission (including an interpretive dance directed, choreographed and stage managed by Trystan) that awards them an all expense paid trip to NYC. Trystan, the ultimate theatre queen of Southern Florida, is psyched. He's always dreamed of flashing his jazz hands on the Great White Way and this may be his chance. Teddy, the resident hypochondriac of the family, can only focus on crime statistics and everything that could possibly go wrong. Their mother encourages them to go on the trip to allow her some quality time with her husband, Mr. Richard, who she recently met on NeedaDaddy. With the help of a New York City guidebook, they map out the adventures that they will embark on. The problem is, they are pretty out of touch with what the big city has in store and run into a myriad of situations that they are ill equipped to handle.

plot: Two adult brothers who still live with their mother in a small town in Florida, are awarded a week long trip to New York City after winning a radio sweepstakes.::Cory Stonebrook
